  "init_eqs": "timeupd = 0;",
  "frame_eqs": "warp=0;\nwave_r=sin(time*4);\nwave_g=sin(time%2);\nwave_b=sin(time/2);\ndy=(sin(time))/60;\nwave_mystery=sin(bass_att/1.5)-0.5;\n\nnormvol = (bass + mid + treb)*0.625; //normalizing the volume\ntimeupd = if(equal(time%0.015, 0), timeupd = timeupd + 1/fps, timeupd); //increments the new value communicated via time variable, fps-independent. Thank you, Nitorami (martin)!\nbeatreset = if(above(timeupd, 0.2) && above(normvol, 2), timeupd = 0, timeupd); //the new time value resets to 0 if the volume is higher than 2 and it passed 0.2 seconds.\n\n\n//--COMP SHADER CONTROL--\nranddistortx = if(below(timeupd, 0.001), rand(5), randdistortx);\nranddistorty = if(below(timeupd, 0.001), rand(5), randdistorty);\n\nq31=randdistortx;\nq32=randdistorty;\n//-----------------------\n\nmonitor = timeupd;",
